Class ObserverRegistry<TypeToReturn>

java.lang.Object
  com.alexgilleran.icesoap.observer.registry.ObserverRegistry<TypeToReturn>
Type Parameters:
TypeToReturn - The type of the object that will be returned from the SOAP call.
Direct Known Subclasses:
ListObserverRegistry
public class ObserverRegistry<TypeToReturn>
extends Object

Helper class that holds a collection of SOAPObservers and allows them all to be notified of events with one call.

Author:
Alex Gilleran

notifyException

public void notifyException(Request<TypeToReturn> request,
                            SOAPException exception)
Notifies all observers of a Request of an Exception that has occurred during request processing. This is necessary due to the complications of passing checked exceptions that happen on a background thread.

Parameters:
request - The request that's hit an exception.
exception - The exception that has occurred.
